{"tid":438710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔汀角路孕婦墮樓　一屍兩命","createTime":"2017-10-17T07:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T08:16:43.000Z","uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ce9ef8068fd31d6dc30c4897ada4870e4072d893","tid":438710,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"大埔汀角路19號富善花園第2座一單位，發生一屍兩命墮樓案。下午1時22分，一名婦人在離開寓所後，被發現從高處墮下，倒臥地上，救護員接報到場，證實婦人已傷重死亡，警方正對案件展開調查。據悉，女事主懷有約20周身孕。"},{"pid":"707a5035fc0ed7c2265867a0de4ffa7f6e2e4b6f","tid":438710,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大埔哩幾日都有份！"},{"pid":"470ef457c437fc0127e9e7665e98a09df8f76063","tid":438710,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"連大肚婆都要跳樓"},{"pid":"9bd8f08b28b9cfdee8144c45f7a3a231bbd620cc","tid":438710,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72eee557af60232dbc97fa50a545fac0586d5d9b","tid":438710,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cccc43bc268c2256001a3cb9d130b06d78813c6","tid":438710,"uid":6577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"事主幾大？"},{"pid":"5948470729b1f7d86f4ef2840c952b0f9f478e71","tid":438710,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事主幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大埔孕婦墮樓釀一屍兩命。下午1時22分，汀角路富善花園2座一名孕婦向母親指有事離家，其後母親聞窗外傳來巨響，落樓查看時，赫見女兒墮樓重傷，倒臥於大廈對開單車停泊處，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報到場，證實婦人已傷重死亡。<br />\n<br />\n現場一名女親友聞噩耗傷心欲絕，需要女警從旁安慰，並取來一張椅子讓她休息，見她受打擊後變得一臉茫然，眼泛淚光。據悉，38歲女事主懷有約20周身孕，有情緒病紀錄，與丈夫同住上址，警方已封鎖現場調查，正向其家人了解事件，調查其墮樓原因。"},{"pid":"e65526b175d9494124703e1325ffa1947a72a5ab","tid":438710,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbae7aef5dc1466f7e83a2abbacff5fadcd963bc","tid":438710,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"17b52148a4f4b9eb13a714ffda0d5a54b3a46cd1","tid":438710,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企附近"},{"pid":"34c39a35121a22ca033039f74de10c1922d14ce4","tid":438710,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"r.i.p \\l/<br />\n兩母子一齊投胎去戶好人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa117a18a53f3c892837db5442c106a68bb815a","tid":438710,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:15:44.000Z","msg":"產前抑鬱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9fc2849328a4dd140b7ee6994ed584256fb852","tid":438710,"uid":131241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企附近</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}